```plantuml
@startuml DJMcK_aws-lake-training

actor User
participant "CloudFormation" as CF
participant "S3 Buckets (Raw/Landing/Curated)" as S3
participant "EMR (Spark)" as EMR
participant "AWS Glue" as Glue
participant "AWS Athena" as Athena
participant "Step Functions" as SF
participant "Lambda Functions" as Lambda
participant "Comprehend Medical" as CM

User -> CF: Deploy lake-buckets.yaml
CF -> S3: Create Raw/Landing/Curated buckets

User -> EMR: Execute fda.01.land.py
EMR -> S3: Read raw FDA data
EMR -> S3: Write transformed data to Landing

User -> EMR: Execute fda.02.curate.py
EMR -> S3: Read from Landing
EMR -> S3: Write curated data to Curated

User -> Glue: Run crawler
Glue -> S3: Scan Curated data
Glue --> Athena: Update metadata catalog

User -> SF: Start Comprehend Medical workflow
SF -> Lambda: Invoke configure_count
Lambda -> Athena: Query count of records
Lambda --> SF: Return count

loop For each batch
    SF -> Lambda: Invoke query_athena
    Lambda -> Athena: Get batch of records
    Lambda --> SF: Return records
    
    SF -> Lambda: Invoke call_comprehend
    Lambda -> CM: Process text for indications
    CM --> Lambda: Return entities
    Lambda -> S3: Store results
    
    SF -> Lambda: Invoke iterator
    Lambda --> SF: Return has_more flag
end

User -> EMR: Execute fda.indications.py
EMR -> S3: Read curated data
EMR -> S3: Read Comprehend results
EMR -> S3: Write final dataset

@enduml
```